data.description: Two Master Bedrooms, one on main level with private master bath.  Another Master Bedroom on first lower level and then a full apartment with full kitchen and 2 more bedrooms and office and living room.  Private exterior entrance.  This home will definitely accommodate 2 families.  It is located on a 4.68 acre lot close to Mall of Georgia. Could possibly build an additional home on site.  Must verify with County. Also included you will find a metal tool shed.   The roof was replaced in 2018.  Completely remodeled inside.  Really a must see if you want a lot of space and privacy.  Inside is impeccable.   House sits back off  street .  Plenty of parking.
